<rss xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" version="2.0"><channel><title>Hugo - Tag - Larry Marzan Jr.</title><link>https://larrymarzanjr.github.io/tags/Hugo/</link><description>Hugo - Tag - Larry Marzan Jr.</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>en-us</language><lastBuildDate>Sun, 06 Nov 2022 21:22:03 +0800</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://larrymarzanjr.github.io/tags/Hugo/" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Instalasi Hugo Dengan Versi Tertentu</title><link>https://larrymarzanjr.github.io/posts/static-site/Instalasi-Hugo-dengan-Versi-Tertentu/</link><pubDate>Sun, 06 Nov 2022 21:22:03 +0800</pubDate><author>Larry Marzan Jr.</author><guid>https://larrymarzanjr.github.io/posts/static-site/Instalasi-Hugo-dengan-Versi-Tertentu/</guid><description><![CDATA[<h3 id="persiapan-install-package-manager-homebrew">Persiapan Install Package Manager Homebrew</h3>
<p>Sebelum instalasi Hugo di Linux, kita perlu menginstall package manager <a href="https://brew.sh/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreffer ">Homebrew</a>. Ikuti perintah pada site tersebut untuk menginstall Homebrew. Masukkan perintah berikut:</p>
<div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;"><code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"><span style="display:flex;"><span>/bin/bash -c <span style="color:#e6db74">&#34;</span><span style="color:#66d9ef">$(</span>curl -fsSL https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Homebrew/install/HEAD/install.sh<span style="color:#66d9ef">)</span><span style="color:#e6db74">&#34;</span>
</span></span></code></pre></div><h3 id="install-hugo-dengan-versi-tertentu">Install Hugo Dengan Versi Tertentu</h3>
<p>Katakanlah misalnya anda ingin menginstal Hugo dengan versi <code>0.62.0</code> maka perintah yang diketik adalah sebagai berikut:</p>
<div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;"><code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"><span style="display:flex;"><span>brew extract --version<span style="color:#f92672">=</span>0.62.0
</span></span></code></pre></div><p>Kemudian lanjutkan install dengan versi Hugo yang anda inginkan</p>
<div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;"><code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"><span style="display:flex;"><span>homebrew/cask brew install hugo@0.62.0
</span></span></code></pre></div><h3 id="referensi">Referensi</h3>
<p><a href="https://github.com/Homebrew/discussions/discussions/2941#discussioncomment-3205121" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreffer ">Github tentang Install specific version of Hugo via Homebrew #2941</a></p>]]></description></item></channel></rss>